Before he became one of the faces of “Dadin Kowa”, a Hausa TV series that runs on Arewa24, Ahmed Bello – who features as Nazir – had been an actor in the Hausa film industry, Kannywood. And prior to that he was achoreographer and counts among actors he taught some dance steps Ali Nuhu and Adam A. Zango. In this video, he speaks about his film career and the challenges faced by filmmakers